HEADWORD: Scaldfish
<hw>Scald"fish`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Scald</ets>, a. + <ets>fish</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A European flounder (<spn>Arnoglossus laterna</spn>, or <spn>Psetta arnoglossa</spn>); -- called also <altname>megrim</altname>, and <altname>smooth sole</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

